OL,3,CMother, 55, spared jailed for killing
OL,4,Cbaby boy almost 30 years ago
OL,6,FA mother who admitted killing her
OL,7,Fnewborn son more than 25 years ago has
OL,8,Fbeen spared jailed after a judge said
OL,9,Fher case called "for compassion".
OL,11,FThe body of baby Callum - named by the
OL,12,Fofficers who worked on the case - was
OL,13,Ffound in a bin bag in woods near
OL,14,FGulliver's World in Warrington in 1998.
OL,16,FJoanne Sharkey, 55, remained
OL,17,Funidentified until 2023, when her
OL,18,Feldest son's DNA was added to the
OL,19,Fpolice database, leading to her arrest.
