OL,4,Cbaby boy almost 30 years ago
OL,6,FThe mum, from Croxteth, in Merseyside,
OL,7,Fdenied murder but pleaded guilty to
OL,8,Fthe lesser charge of manslaughter on
OL,9,Fthe basis of diminished responsibility
OL,10,Fand concealing the birth of a child.
OL,12,FSentencing her at Liverpool Crown
OL,13,FCourt, Mrs Justice Eady told her she
OL,14,Fwas satisfied "depression and the
OL,15,Ftrauma of the birth substantially
OL,16,Fimpaired your ability to understand
OL,17,Fthe nature and consequences of your
OL,18,Factions."
