OL,6,FBut she later added: "I am satisfied
OL,7,Fthat this very sad case calls for
OL,8,Fcompassion, no useful purpose would be
OL,9,Fachieved by immediate imprisonment.
OL,11,F"I consider that appropriate
OL,12,Fpunishment can be achieved by a
OL,13,Fcustodial term that is suspended."
OL,15,FSharkey was seen shaking and in tears
OL,16,Fas she was handed the sentence.
OL,18,FShe was also given a rehabilitation
OL,19,Factivity requirement of up to 30 days
OL,20,Fand a 12-month mental health treatment
OL,21,Frequirement.
