OL,6,FLiverpool Crown Court previously heard
OL,7,Fthe body of the infant was found in a
OL,8,Fbin bag by walkers on 14 March 1998.
OL,10,FDetectives named the infant Callum,
OL,11,Fafter the suburb where he was found
OL,12,Fdead, and was believed to have been
OL,13,Fjust a few hours old.
OL,15,FThe court heard when Sharkey killed
OL,16,Fthe baby, she was suffering from post-
OL,17,Fnatal depression after the birth of
OL,18,Fher first son, Matthew, in 1996.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
