OL,6,FMr Hankin said psychiatrists agreed
OL,7,FSharkey was "fearful of becoming a
OL,8,Fmother to another child" and developed
OL,9,Fa depressive illness which
OL,10,F"substantially impaired (her) ability
OL,11,Fto form rational judgement and
OL,12,Fexercise self-control".
OL,14,FShe told police she kept her pregnancy
OL,15,Fa secret and, when the baby was born
OL,16,Fin the bathroom of her house in
OL,17,FCroxteth, Liverpool, she heard him
OL,18,Fstarting to make a noise and covered
OL,19,Fhis nose and mouth "to make him quiet".
